collectible.description: "Tiger Head and Lantern Snowman" New Year is coming, a little snowman with a tiger head hat from Ting DAO brought this lantern lamp to send blessings and New Year's love.

collectible.name: Chinese Red: Year of the Tiger SE left-by pixelgalaxy1 from Wearable Dao
collectible.author: 0x142f3717b640619bc4856bb5e39ecc8405116d04
collectible.description: Year of the Tiger is a special edition designed to celebrate the Chinese Year of the Tiger. The left and right uppers are combined into a tiger head, the left shoe has the English word "TIGER" on the outside, and the right foot has the Chinese word "虎". Tiger stripes on the inside of the shoe.

collectible.name: Chinese Red: VEST (Year of the Tiger) -by pixelgalaxy1 from Wearable Dao
collectible.author: 0x142f3717b640619bc4856bb5e39ecc8405116d04
collectible.description:
The Year of the Tiger series is a special edition of the Year of the Tiger Cryptovoxel Vox designed for the "China Red" themed event. The colors are Chinese red and gold, while highlighting the tiger theme of the Chinese Year of the Tiger. Series of works by the head, vest, shorts, shoes, wings of five parts, intended to wish you the year of the tiger "tiger with wings".

The front of the vest has a tiger face; On the back of the tiger skin markings, inlaid the Chinese word"虎"

collectible.name: Chinese Red: HEAD (Year of the Tiger) -by pixelgalaxy1 from Wearable Dao
collectible.author: 0x142f3717b640619bc4856bb5e39ecc8405116d04
collectible.description: The head of the tiger, celebrating the arrival of the Year of the Tiger in China, at the same time, the design of the tiger head also has the majesty and ferocity of the tiger as the king of beasts, the back of the head has the Chinese word "虎" logo, is also one of the symbols of the whole series.

collectible.name: Chinese Red: SHORTS (Year of the Tiger) -by pixelgalaxy1 from Wearable Dao
collectible.author: 0x142f3717b640619bc4856bb5e39ecc8405116d04
collectible.description: The English "TIGER" print is prominent on the front of the shorts, with a TIGER skin stripe across the leg. The design of the tiger tail on the back of the shorts completes the tiger element and also adds a little cuteness and naughtiness.
